channel.title: How about a ::kill [playername] Command?!?! Can Anyone help
channel.description:
Well, i was wondering if anyone knew how to make a command that killed the player its aimed at (EX: ::kill Patchumz), I would like to have it for fun, and for the fact that going and manually editing people's characters cuz they picked up something they weren't supposed to is annoying (And the occasional rule breaker :P).
Just post if you can help me, please don't spam my thread :$
